While our processing of Personal Information varies based upon our relationship and interactions with
                you, the table below identifies, generally, the categories of Personal Information that we have
                collected about California residents in the prior twelve (12) months, as well as the categories of third
                parties to whom we may disclose this Personal Information for a business or commercial purpose. For more
                information about the business and commercial purposes, for which we may disclose your Personal
                Information, please see the
Sharing of Information
section
                above and the Purposes for Collecting, Using, Disclosing, and Processing Personal Information below.
